-- Thales says not involved in Alstom Transport issue
-- By Cyril Altmeyer
-- Wed May 14, 2014 06:19AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, May 14 (Reuters) - Thales <TCFP.PA> is not involved in discussions surrounding Alstom's <ALSO.PA> transport business, the chief executive of Europe's largest defence electronics group by sales said on Wednesday.

La Lettre de l'Expansion newsletter reported on Monday that Economy Minister Arnaud Montebourg had contacted various companies such as Thales to find ways to reinforce the transport unit should General Electric <GE.N> buy Alstom's power businesses.